author: Aaron Katersky, Ella Torres
title: At least 26 New York City homeless, among hundreds of cases, have died from COVID-19
description: Mayor Bill de Blasio recently announced new protections for the homeless.
content:
At least 26 homeless people among the 421 confirmed to have COVID-19 in New York City had died as of Tuesday, city officials said.
